    "engine": "knitr",
    "markdown": "\n::: {.cell}\n\n:::\n\n\n# Patchwork\n\n<center>\n![](images/ggplot2_patchwork.png){style=\"width:200px\"}\n</center>\n\nThe `patchwork` package allows you to combine multiple ggplots into one graphic.\n\nIt is a separate package to `tidyverse` and requires installing.\nThe install instructions are in the below link.\n\n[Patchwork home page](https://patchwork.data-imaginist.com/)\n\nOnce installed you can load the library.\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\nlibrary(\"patchwork\")\n```\n:::\n\n\n## Dataset\n\nFor demonstration we'll load the `mushroom_tbl` data from the [mgrtibbles package](/datasets/mgrtibbles.qmd) (hyperlink includes install instructions).\nFor easier plot visualisation we'll subsample the data.\n\n[mushroom_tbl details](https://github.com/m-gemmell/mgrtibbles/wiki/mushroom_tbl)\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n\n```{.r .cell-code}\n#Subsampled dataset\n#Set seed for random sampling\nset.seed(\"483\")\nmushroom_tbl <- mgrtibbles::mushroom_tbl |>\n    #Random sample of 150 rows\n    dplyr::slice_sample(n = 150, replace=FALSE)\n#Reset random seed to normal operation\nset.seed(NULL)\n```\n:::\n\n\n\n<div class='webex-solution'><button>View mushroom_tbl contents</button>\n\n\n::: {.cell}\n::: {.cell-output-display}\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"reactable html-widget html-fill-item\" id=\"htmlwidget-0e3f26c45786ace2e281\" style=\"width:auto;height:auto;\"></div>\n<script type=\"application/json\" data-for=\"htmlwidget-0e3f26c45786ace2e281\">{\"x\":{\"tag\":{\"name\":\"Reactable\",\"attribs\":{\"data\":{\"class\":[\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"poisonous\",\"edible\",\"edible\",\"poisonous\",\"edible